{
  "title": "Charon — Arrow data mover",
  "uid": "charon-moves",
  "tags": ["kantheon", "charon", "data-plane"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Moves/s by pair + result",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (source, target, result) (rate(charon_moves_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{source}}→{{target}} ({{result}})"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Move duration p50/p95/p99 (ms)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le, source, target) (rate(charon_move_duration_ms_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50 {{source}}→{{target}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, source, target) (rate(charon_move_duration_ms_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{source}}→{{target}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le, source, target) (rate(charon_move_duration_ms_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99 {{source}}→{{target}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Error rate by pair",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (source, target) (rate(charon_moves_total{result=\"error\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{source}}→{{target}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Fingerprint-mismatch (PD-5 drift) /s",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (source, target) (rate(charon_fingerprint_mismatch_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{source}}→{{target}}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "_notes": [
    "Metrics: charon_moves_total{rpc,source,target,result}, charon_move_duration_ms (timer w/ percentile histogram), charon_fingerprint_mismatch_total{source,target}.",
    "Trace nesting: charon-mcp + the gRPC server are OTel-instrumented (ktor-opentelemetry + grpc context propagation); a Charon move appears as a child span under the caller's trace (Pythia investigation → Charon move). Verified from a fixture caller; live propagation in the integration suite."
  ]
}
